### Identify Potential Infinite Loops
Look for `for`/`while` loops over dynamic data without hard gas-safe limits.

```solidity
// Unbounded loop can run out of gas
function distribute() external {
    for (uint256 i = 0; i < recipients.length; i++) {
        token.transfer(recipients[i], amount);
    }
}
```

**Invariant:** Batch in chunks, cap `recipients.length`, or use pull-based claiming.
